  });

};

/**
 * Creates a tree like structure from an arbitrary collection of elements
 *
 * @example
 * tree: {
 *	0: [
 *		{ id: 'shape_12da', priority: 1, ... },
 *		{ id: 'shape_01bj', priority: 1, ... },
 *		{ id: 'connection_79fa', source: 'shape_12da', target: 'shape_01bj', priority: 3, ... },
 *	],
